{"word":"G1570 - ἔκθετος - ékthetos - ek'-thet-os - Cast out","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔκθετος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ékthetos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek'-thet-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cast out</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வெளியே போட்டுவிடு - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"cast out, exposed"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5087 - τίθημι - títhēmi - tith'-ay-mee/5087\">G5087</a>; <i>put out</i>, that is, <i>exposed</i> to perish: - cast out.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}